{"tid":1984594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場 - 陳彥霖逝世 7 個月．已忘？已散？","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T14:38:23.000Z","uid":60259,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6db9e7ead5fc75021690e53ac127e99e0f6ab39d","tid":1984594,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"今天是知專設計學院女學生陳彥霖逝世的 7 個月，在將軍澳尚德邨外的公祭區，孤燭依舊，壇前更見岑寂。未知是否受疫情及天氣影響，未見有人致祭獻花。<br />\n<br />\n7 個月前的 22 日，15 歲的陳彥霖被發現全身赤裸浮屍於油塘魔鬼山一帶海面，警方稱調查後認為死因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3021457634606503/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3021457634606503%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=95240358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3021457634606503/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c1c19a71b338adf2777bb9da61c94936f5e06e5f","tid":1984594,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"18b3a78873c3cc98476c5293d9e90bdb0adac3f9","tid":1984594,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"好多手足黎上香wo"},{"pid":"f5712ae88509d3c139a2cc90fd2c4f02beb3af35","tid":1984594,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b3a78873c3cc98476c5293d9e90bdb0adac3f9","tid":1984594,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"好多手足黎上香wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"Just copy from stand news"},{"pid":"ffbdb16cad85388f057ce757f2821e146a27e39b","tid":1984594,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e3a1e7d173e14acd5894ca3967a9ea8ea0904b","tid":1984594,"u